The $26 Stay Connected Plan includes:
• 12GB of Main Data
• 7GB App allotment for:  Music, Video YouTube, TikTok, BiP, Loop, SportsMax and GoLoud
• Unlimited Local Voice
• Unlimited calls to 1 US/CA # or Regional Digicel number (excluding Jamaica)
• Valid for 14 days
